event.title: 在北京申请签证（中文版）
event.description:
预约：在政府官方 App 上预约办理时间（预约有效期为明天）。
现场办理：到达办事大厅，进行拍照并采集指纹信息。
材料提交：提交申请表及身份证。
领取方式：通过 EMS 快递寄送护照（时间：约 7 个工作日）。
event.description_en:
Appointment: Make an appointment through the official government app (the appointment is valid until tomorrow).
On-site processing: Arrive at the service hall to have your photo taken and fingerprints collected.
Document submission: Submit the application form and identification card.
Collection method: The passport will be delivered via EMS express (processing time: approximately 7 working days).

event.title: 在北京申请签证(红色官僚主义中文版)
event.description:
1.“号源”博弈：尝试线上预约，但未来一个月的名额全部约满。
＜障碍：资源稀缺／准入受限＞
＜应对方式：找“黄牛”代抢，或在午夜不断刷新页面＞
2.现场被退回：到达办事大厅后，被告知照片背景“蓝得不够标准”。
＜障碍：自由裁量与随意性＞
＜成本：被迫在指定照相点重新拍照（价格偏高）＞
3. 材料循环：提交申请表后，工作人员要求提供 App 清单中未列出的“户口本”页面。
＜障碍：信息不对称＞
＜应对方式：回家取材料＞
＜成本：额外耗时 1 天＞
4. “解释权”陷阱：携带材料再次前往时，新的工作人员表示前一位工作人员的解释不正确，要求先到当地派出所办理并加盖另一种公章。
＜障碍：执法标准不一致＞
＜成本：挫败感／困惑＞
5. 提交成功：最终完成材料提交。
6. 领取结果：收到护照，但因“政治活动安保审查”，办理时间延长至 15 天。
event.description_en:
1. The “Number” Game: Try to book online, but all slots are full for the next month.
<Barrier: Scarcity of Access> <Action: Use “Scalper” (黄牛) or refresh page at midnight>
2. On-site Rejection: Arrived at the hall, but was told the photo background was “not blue enough”.
<Barrier: Arbitrary Discretion> <Cost: Re-take photo at specific booth (expensive)>
3. Document Loop: Submit the form. Officer demands a “Hukou” (Household Register) page that wasn’t on the app’s checklist.
<Barrier: Information Asymmetry> <Action: Go home to fetch document> <Cost: 1 extra day>
4. The “Interpretation” Trap: Return with the document. The new officer says the previous officer’s interpretation was wrong, and you need a different stamp from the local police station first.
<Barrier: Inconsistent Enforcement> <Cost: Frustration/Confusion>
5. Submission: Finally submit materials.
6. Collection: Receive passport <Time: Delayed to 15 days due to “Political Event Security Check”>.
